# CSV2Sendy

<div align="center">

[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/csv2sendy.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/csv2sendy)
[![Python Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.9-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org/downloads/release/python-390/)
